reviewText: Product is as described. However I am in America and cannot play so it will just collect dust on my shelf until I get a dvd player that will play it or sell it.

Doesn't work in any territory but Ireland.. won't exchange or refund if you open.. in little fine print it tells you this.. feel like this is something that should be in title! Would have left 0 stars if I could

I didn't realize that this set would be region locked, apparently unless I'm in Ireland, I can't watch it on anything but my computer, doesn't work on a blu-ray player, DVD player, ps3, ps4, or Xbox 360. If you don't live in ireland, don't buy it
Be sure and read fine print...this DVD works on foreign DVD players.....if u accidentally order this product don't take the wrapping off it bc they WILL NOT REFUND YOUR MONEY!!!!!!!!!!!!!
It is another region so it doesn't play justa waste of money.
